SUMMARY:GRATIS KONZERT: NEST (us) + URBAN MISERY (aut)
LOCATION:Arena
DESCRIPTION:Roadtrip To Outta Space | Arena Wien - Dreiraum | Early Show / Curfew 22 Uhr / FREIER EINTRITT!  19:00 Doors 20:00 Urban Misery 21:00 Nest  Nest (ex Pig Destroyer) is the sonic embodiment of catharsis and confrontation. Spearheaded by vocalist/guitarist John Jarvis (Scour\, Agoraphobic Nosebleed)\, Nest fuses industrial precision with shoegaze melancholy and hardcore abrasion. Their fourth LP\, Endeavors\, released via Housecore Records\, channels grief\, rage\, and resilience into a tightly wound 10-track assault. For Fans of Helmet\, Hum\, Deftones and Quicksand.  https://nestofficial.bandcamp.com/  Urban Misery: https://urbanmisery.bandcamp.com/ 
URL:https://arena.wien/Home/Programm-Detail/concert-id/48555
